 *   - item: An array of information about the field_collection_item to display.
 *   - content: An array of content of field collection items to display.
 *   - index:  An array index of the field_collection_item to display.
 *   - entity: The content entity with limited access to object properties and methods.
 *     Only method names starting with "get", "has", or "is" and a few common
